df = []
for expt, g in group.items():
    
    diam = g.attrs.get('diameter')
    diam_r = g.attrs.get('diameterR')
    
    num = len(set(diam))
    if diam_r is None:
        repeat = False
        num_r = None
        consistent = num == 1

        num_r = len(set(diam_r))
        consistent = num == num_r

    df.append({
        'expt': [expt],
        'num_diam': [num],
        'num_diam_r': [num_r],
        'consistent': [consistent],
    })
